{
  "stem": "4345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "If they will find us, they will kill us, and then we will be lost somewhere and I-- I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So she says, you know, [SPEAKING POLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They said in Poland, you know, back-- a goat goes backwards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But I said, in my case, we are not goats, I said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I-- I'm not-- I don't want to die here like a dog in someplace, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And so we start at the very same forest that I went with the bus.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I just went there in April of 1923-- 1923, April.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- April 23rd, '95.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Oy vey is me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I'm so famished at this point already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we meet a guy on a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The forest is not the same because they already built homes there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They removed-- but the road is there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he said-- and I ask them both, [SPEAKING GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Where is the camp that the haftling girl came yesterday?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he told me, [SPEAKING GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we told him that we fell off the truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The truck was crowded and that we fell off and [GERMAN], we are going there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So he came-- he told us where to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Now, the pictures, the little pictures that you have there, I'd like to explain it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I had this on my neck, OK?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I had the pictures on my neck that I took from home when the Nazis came in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I didn't run for the gold, which we didn't have anyway, I ran for pictures.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I thought, whatever happens, let me have pictures of my family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I made myself a little sack myself on a rope and I had this on my neck all through the six years, OK?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
